<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 space-y-10">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <div class="border-b border-luxury-200 pb-8 space-y-2">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-800 border border-emerald-200 text-[10px] font-display font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
            <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-600"></i> Legal & Data Protection Compliance
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-luxury-950">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xs text-luxury-500 font-mono">Effective Date: July 22, 2026 | Deenz Organics, Wanpora, Kulgam, J&K - 192231</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Policy Highlights Banner -->
    <div class="bg-emerald-50/80 border border-emerald-200/80 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 space-y-3 shadow-2xs">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-sm text-emerald-950 uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center gap-2">
            <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700"></i> Our Customer Privacy Promise
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-emerald-900 leading-relaxed">
            At Deenz Organics (Main Office: Wanpora, Kulgam, Jammu & Kashmir - 192231), we respect your trust above all else. We collect only the essential information needed to fulfill and dispatch your single-origin organic harvest orders across India and internationally. We <strong>never sell, rent, trade, or leak</strong> your personal contact details to external marketing agencies or third parties.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Sections -->
    <div class="space-y-8 text-xs sm:text-sm text-luxury-700 leading-relaxed">
        
        <section class="space-y-3 bg-white border border-luxury-200/70 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-2xs">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-base text-luxury-950 border-b border-luxury-100 pb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600"></span> 1. Information We Collect
            </h2>
            <p>When you browse our platform, place an order, or send an inquiry, we collect the following limited details:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-xs text-luxury-600">
                <li><strong>Identity & Delivery Credentials:</strong> Full name, complete delivery address, landmark, PIN code, email address, and contact phone number.</li>
                <li><strong>Order & Transaction History:</strong> Commodity selection (e.g., Kashmiri Walnut Kernels, Mountain Garlic Cloves), package weight variants, invoice ID, and live delivery status.</li>
                <li><strong>Customer Support Logs:</strong> Messages, feedback, or review comments submitted directly through our contact form or WhatsApp hotline.</li>
                <li><strong>Technical Diagnostics:</strong> Anonymized IP addresses, browser types, and session tokens to protect against cross-site request forgery (CSRF) and checkout fraud.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3 bg-white border border-luxury-200/70 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-2xs">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-base text-luxury-950 border-b border-luxury-100 pb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600"></span> 2. How Your Data Is Utilized
            </h2>
            <p>Your information is used strictly for legitimate e-commerce operations:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-xs text-luxury-600">
                <li>Processing, vacuum packaging, and dispatching orders directly from our central sorting unit in Wanpora, Kulgam, J&K.</li>
                <li>Sending real-time order confirmation receipts and live courier tracking links via SMS, WhatsApp, and Email.</li>
                <li>Providing direct founder customer support for 100% crunch replacement claims or delivery inquiries.</li>
                <li>Validating promotional discount codes (such as <code>KASHMIR10</code> or <code>ORGANIC50</code>).</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3 bg-white border border-luxury-200/70 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-2xs">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-base text-luxury-950 border-b border-luxury-100 pb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600"></span> 3. Financial Data & Payment Gateway Security
            </h2>
            <p>We prioritize complete financial transaction security:</p>
            <div class="bg-stone-50 border border-stone-200/80 rounded-xl p-4 text-xs space-y-2 text-stone-700">
                <p>
                    All online payment processing is executed via 256-bit encrypted, PCI-DSS Level 1 certified payment gateways (e.g., <strong>Razorpay Gateway</strong>). 
                </p>
                <p class="font-bold text-stone-900">
                    Deenz Organics NEVER stores, views, or records your full credit/debit card details, bank account passwords, or UPI PINs on our servers.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3 bg-white border border-luxury-200/70 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-2xs">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-base text-luxury-950 border-b border-luxury-100 pb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600"></span> 4. Trusted Courier Partners
            </h2>
            <p>To deliver fresh mountain harvests swiftly across 19,000+ pincodes in India, we share delivery address details exclusively with licensed logistics partners (e.g., BlueDart, Delhivery, Express Air Cargo, India Post). These partners are legally restricted from using your phone number or address for any purpose other than executing delivery.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="space-y-3 bg-white border border-luxury-200/70 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-2xs">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-base text-luxury-950 border-b border-luxury-100 pb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-600"></span> 5. Your Rights & Data Officer Contact
            </h2>
            <p>Under Indian Information Technology legislation and international privacy regulations, you retain full ownership of your data. You may request account deletion or data modification at any time by contacting our Privacy Officer:</p>
            
            <div class="bg-luxury-900 text-luxury-100 rounded-xl p-5 text-xs space-y-1.5 border border-luxury-800 shadow-sm mt-3">
                <h4 class="font-display font-bold text-sm text-amber-300 uppercase tracking-wider">Privacy & Grievance Officer</h4>
                <p class="font-semibold text-white">Deenz Organics Headquarters</p>
                <p class="text-luxury-300">Wanpora, Kulgam, Jammu & Kashmir - 192231, India</p>
                <p class="text-luxury-200 font-mono pt-1">
                    Direct Founders: Dr. Deen Mohd & Raashid Din
                </p>
                <p class="text-amber-300 font-mono">
                    Email: dr.deenmohd@gmail.com | Phone: +91 60060 49016
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>
</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
